cast.overview: A widow with three children hires a handyman to fix her house during a major storm. When not doing home repairs, he shares his philosophy of believing in the power of the universe to deliver what we want.
cast.title: The Secret: Dare to Dream

Aidan is an American child/teenage actor, internet personality, and social media presence. He is famous for The Punisher (TV Series) 2017, New Amsterdam (TV Series) 2021, City on a Hill (TV Series) 2022, and The Watcher (TV Mini-Series) 2022.

Actor Aidan Pierce Brennan was born in California, United States on March 28, 2008. This American actress's full name is Aidan Pierce Brennan, and her nickname is Aidan.
